This level of personalization not only keeps users engaged but also enhances their overall experience. Netflix reports that 80% of the shows people watch are influenced by its recommendation system. By employing AI for personalized messaging and recommendations, Netflix has transformed the way we consume content, showcasing the power of AI in outbound marketing.

